description: |
  <p>
  Example plugin that can write OTIO files supported by otio from within rv. This is
  meant only as proof of concept.
  </p>
  <p>
  To create the package run:
  </p>
  <p>
  zip example_otio_writer_plugin-1.0.rvpkg PACKAGE example_otio_writer_plugin.py otio_writer.py

